data.text: Delve into the creative process of acclaimed director Christopher Nolan in his latest and highly anticipated feature Inception, starring Leonardo DiCaprio, Marion Cotillard, Joseph Gordon-Levitt, and Ken Watanabe. Inception: The Shooting Script offers Nolan's screenplay along with rare insights into his writing process, storyboards, and creative vision.
